      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find that has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep showroom shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been kept in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest standards. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
