    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this absolute beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s completely spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and drives like a dream, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a superlative 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive widebody specimen in pristine condition. This 996.2 is powered by a mid-mounted 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering power through a Getrag 6-speed manual transaxle. The IMS bearing has been proactively upgraded with a dual-row ceramic solution, and the rear main seal (RMS) is verified dry. The chassis dynamics are factory-perfect, featuring a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system and original Bilstein-tuned suspension. Braking performance is anchored by 4-piston monoblock Brembo calipers over cross-drilled rotors with no discernible heat checking. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with uniform paint meter readings and zero rock chips. This is an electronically and mechanically flawless example for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
