      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in a state that can only be described as showroom-fresh. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium upholstery shows zero signs of wear or creasing, and every control and button retains its original tactile crispness. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively maintained at authorized service centers with a full, documented history. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. This sale includes all original manuals, two factory keys, and a clean title. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
